            "title": "Referral for high risk breast specialty evaluation",
            "description": "Refer to high risk breast specialist to discuss primary risk reduction interventions such as chemoprevention.\n\nWomen at greater risk, such as those with at least a 3% risk for breast cancer in the next 5 years, are likely to derive more benefit than harm from risk-reducing medications.",
